    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Mastersystem Infotama Tbk engages in the provision of information and communication technology infrastructure solutions and system integration services to enterprise banking, oil and gas, enterprise, and telecommunication markets in Indonesia. The company offers data center and cloud infrastructure, digital business management, enterprise collaboration, adaptive security architecture, data and AI, telco network solutions, as well as Cloud solutions. It also provides services, including Implementation Service, such as general, migration, and relocation services; maintenance; and managed services. In addition, it offers MS-Insight, an app providing real-time visibility, automation and remediation; MSXperience, a web-based application that provides video portal, webcast, dashboard usage, and analytic report; MS-CDX, a customer experience-oriented dashboard; Mastersystem Sustainability Optimization (MSSO) application; Mastersystem Secure Sphere (MS3), a blackbox security testing solution; AmanTerus, an innovative app designed to protect devices from various threats; and MANTRA AI, a smart digital assistant solution. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Jakarta Pusat, Indonesia.",
